data.title: Resistance Ibiza — TPi
data.meta_description: The Ultra Worldwide brand, Resistance, has teamed up with Visionlite to work on Ibiza’s biggest club production of the summer. Resistance Ibiza, hosted in the world famous Privilege nightclub, ran for 2 months and offered audiences an immersive visual experience. TPi spoke to Visionlite’s Adam Gaca about the project… Photos: Courtesy of Resistance https://resistanceibiza.com/ http://visionlite.eu/ […]
